{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h2 id=\"math-对象的扩展\"><a href=\"#math-%E5%AF%B9%E8%B1%A1%E7%9A%84%E6%89%A9%E5%B1%95\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Math 对象的扩展</h2>\n<p>ES6 在 Math 对象上新增了 17 个与数学相关的方法。所有这些方法都是静态方法，只能在 Math 对象上调用。</p>\n<h3 id=\"mathtrunc\"><a href=\"#mathtrunc\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Math.trunc()</h3>\n<p>Math.trunc方法用于去除一个数的小数部分，返回整数部分。\n</p>\n<h3 id=\"mathsign\"><a href=\"#mathsign\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Math.sign()</h3>\n<p>Math.sign方法用来判断一个数到底是正数、负数、还是零。对于非数值，会先将其转换为数值。</p>\n<p>它会返回五种值。</p>\n<p>参数为正数，返回+1；\n参数为负数，返回-1；\n参数为 0，返回0；\n参数为-0，返回-0;\n其他值，返回NaN。</p>\n<h2 id=\"仅为个人读书笔记，原书-httpes6ruanyifengcom\"><a href=\"#%E4%BB%85%E4%B8%BA%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E8%AF%BB%E4%B9%A6%E7%AC%94%E8%AE%B0%EF%BC%8C%E5%8E%9F%E4%B9%A6-httpes6ruanyifengcom\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>仅为个人读书笔记，原书 <a href=\"http://es6.ruanyifeng.com/\">http://es6.ruanyifeng.com/</a></h2>","timeToRead":1,"excerpt":"Math 对象的扩展 ES6 在 Math 对象上新增了 17 个与数学相关的方法。所有这些方法都是静态方法，只能在 Math 对象上调用。 Math.trunc() Math.trunc方法用于去除一个数的小数部分，返回整数部分。\n     Math.sign() Math…","frontmatter":{"title":"数值的扩展","cover":null,"date":"2018-12-05T10:00:00.000Z","category":"books","tags":["books"]},"fields":{"nextTitle":"let 和 const 命令","nextSlug":"/books/ECMAScript6/1-let-and-const/","prevTitle":"变量的结构赋值","prevSlug":"/books/ECMAScript6/2-destructuring/","slug":"/books/ECMAScript6/6-number/","date":"2018-12-04T16:00:00.000Z"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/books/ECMAScript6/6-number/"}}